{"text_id":166586,"tokens":["The"," Electoral"," College"," system"," in"," the"," United"," States"," presidential"," elections"," has"," long"," been"," a"," topic"," of"," debate","."," On"," one"," hand",","," supporters"," argue"," that"," it"," protects"," small"," states"," and"," preserves"," federal","ism","."," On"," the"," other"," hand",","," critics"," argue"," that"," it"," can"," lead"," to"," an"," und","em","ocratic"," outcome"," and"," ignore"," the"," will"," of"," the"," majority","."," This"," essay"," will"," discuss"," the"," advantages"," and"," disadvantages"," of"," the"," Electoral"," College"," system",","," drawing"," on"," two"," articles"," that"," present"," contrasting"," perspectives"," on"," the"," issue",".","\n\n","One"," advantage"," of"," the"," Electoral"," College"," system",","," as"," highlighted"," in"," an"," article"," by"," Robert"," Hard","away"," published"," in"," The"," Hill",","," is"," its"," ability"," to"," provide"," a"," voice"," for"," smaller"," states","."," Under"," the"," Electoral"," College",","," each"," state"," is"," given"," a"," certain"," number"," of"," electoral"," votes",","," which"," is"," determined"," by"," its"," representation"," in"," Congress","."," This"," means"," that"," even"," the"," smallest"," states",","," such"," as"," Wyoming",","," have"," a"," proportionate"," say"," in"," the"," presidential"," election","."," Without"," the"," Electoral"," College",","," it"," is"," argued"," that"," candidates"," would"," only"," focus"," on"," larger",","," more"," populous"," states",","," neglecting"," the"," concerns"," and"," interests"," of"," smaller"," states",".","\n\n","However",","," there"," are"," several"," disadvantages"," to"," the"," Electoral"," College"," system",","," as"," pointed"," out"," by"," Hendrik"," Hertz","berg"," in"," The"," New"," Yorker","."," One"," major"," criticism"," is"," that"," it"," can"," lead"," to"," an"," und","em","ocratic"," outcome"," wher